{
  "texts": [
    "Lastly, bots will harness the multi-modal capabilities of more advanced generative models.",
    "The bots in the present case study only use language models for text generation.",
    "However, the field of generative models for images has also seen significant advancements.",
    "For instance, Generative Adversarial Networks can already create realistic human faces (Karras et al., 2019 (Karras et al.,, 2020)) that humans fail to identify (Nightingale and Farid, 2022), while the stable diffusion algorithms are capable of producing a variety of images (Rombach et al., 2022).",
    "A combination of autonomy and multimodal capabilities of the generative models can further enhance the potency of malicious social bots."
  ]
}